  "seoSummary": "Evidence in the World Skills Protocol (WSP) is an immutable, verifiable professional fact issued by an authorized Issuer and linked to a Professional Passport. Unlike a credential or a trust score, Evidence records only what was demonstrated, by whom, against which skills framework, and when — enabling independent, reproducible verification without depending on the issuer.",
